Program: Outlook
Title: The Best of Outlook 2013 - Part Two
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p01n9h20
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 27 Dec 2013
Another chance to hear some more of our most inspiring and popular stories from 2013 including: the young Pakistani woman who overcame prejudice to follow her dream of becoming a top squash player; the son of an American anthropologist and a woman from an isolated tribe from the Amazon rainforest on tracking down his mother after 20 years apart; and Omotola Ekeinde - the Queen of Nollywood who has starred in over 300 films. Show less